TopicTitle: Working SSTU for 64-bit KSP version 1.0.4 or later

Articles.Content: Hi! I am trying to get a working version of SSTU for Windows 7 64-bit ksp. In early 1.0.5 i had one, but can't find the copy. :-(. I have tried versions as early as December of 2015, and many after that, but the closest i have gotten is an empty category on the parts category (underneath science) saying 'SSTU Engine Clusters'. It shows different SSTU parts being loaded, but they simply are not anywhere. Anyone have anything?
